{"tid":863614,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【九西補選】民協呼籲支持者全投李卓人：集中票源才有機會贏保皇黨","createTime":"2018-10-15T17:43:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-15T19:51:48.000Z","uid":103156,"like":14,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"deecbfef18181bf276dabca8e7ff7508681f5cdd","tid":863614,"uid":103156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T17:43:17.000Z","msg":"【九西補選】民協呼籲支持者全投李卓人：集中票源才有機會贏保皇黨<br />\n <a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20181016&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=58798839\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20181016%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D58798839&d=Ugl%2BH%2FtrGUxrzRmi98KOvf755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=3fb80075\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20181016%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D58798839&h=d706cf9e\" target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20181016&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=58798839</a><br />\n<br />\n民協聲明指，至今認為初選能最有效處理Plan B問題，並對於民主派未能協調進行初選，表示極度遺憾。然而面對資源豐厚的建制陣營，<span style=\"color: red;\">民協認為民主派必須集中票源才有機會戰勝保皇黨，因此民協決定支持李卓人代表民主派出戰11月25日的立法會九龍西選舉。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">民協又強烈呼籲各位民主同路人，停止對馮檢基的攻擊</span>，因為攻擊無助民主派的選情，只有團結才能有勝利的可能。民協又懇請支持民主的市民，特別是民協的支持者，11月25日「一定要出來投票支持李卓人，一齊反DQ，抗威權，為民主派取回應有的一席！」"},{"pid":"285068e6dad7bfdc4333ac1cf2e9374eebc64293","tid":863614,"uid":83344,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T17:52:03.000Z","msg":"成班On 撚9<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3056dd8b981d65d2743c368e12f2b5452decb373","tid":863614,"uid":35070,"like":4,"dislike":4,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T17:53:09.000Z","msg":"唔怪得馮檢基要走<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3f5f5574e1fbd982830b8861f93140657a4adf7","tid":863614,"uid":125193,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T18:06:36.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>100% DQ李卓人</strong></span>  <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/14.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"237a243a1ef820028a967f43f3e0958cfc33b3a1","tid":863614,"uid":3510,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T18:21:21.000Z","msg":"欺師滅祖垃圾黨 執柒咗佢啦"},{"pid":"c1c240c816a6b1a5bb31742f1a90cd67b39d2dfb","tid":863614,"uid":189,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T18:44:18.000Z","msg":"劉穎匡嗰陣畀梁頌恆支持都可以係DQ 理據，睇怕今次可能真係要出到基哥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f1a83d831cf740d9348babfb3f91b95d235df7c","tid":863614,"uid":66324,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T19:50:26.000Z","msg":"不如搵個港獨派endorse李卓人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b920635429cbfdbfcf5d5399cfe9ff099c4422c4","tid":863614,"uid":111253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5f1a83d831cf740d9348babfb3f91b95d235df7c","tid":863614,"uid":66324,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T19:50:26.000Z","msg":"不如搵個港獨派endorse李卓人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T19:51:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}